    public class Sensitometry
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, danfulea.math.numerical.Function
    Film sensitometry QC test. It involves computation of: base + fog, the contrast, film speed, latitude and the sensitometric HD curve.
    Author:
    Dan Fulea, 28 Apr. 2015
